{"tid":1215301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【1428】南華早報記者 Alvin Lum 指，有兩名抗爭者昨晚在伊利沙伯醫院，被警方以暴動罪拘捕。","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:49:11.000Z","uid":5843,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c01fdf9bf32a4adae75c0b51bd345a3eda2d50d0","tid":1215301,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"【1428】南華早報記者 Alvin Lum 指，有兩名抗爭者昨晚在伊利沙伯醫院，被警方以暴動罪拘捕。二人曾向醫護人員表示去過金鐘，傷口是在衝突中造成。<br />\n<br />\n大家記住大掃除，將舊衫舊褲扔走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277199f5b66a59fea52a052d3738a2e63754f13c","tid":1215301,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:43:06.000Z","msg":"係屋企整親"},{"pid":"2936a63b37de38a85efef83650ad1e8281bca529","tid":1215301,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"277199f5b66a59fea52a052d3738a2e63754f13c","tid":1215301,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:43:06.000Z","msg":"係屋企整親"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:43:36.000Z","msg":"啲洋蔥搞到我喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da98e8239d5c4ec3aac9cb25a6fb202e6f827095","tid":1215301,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpsuVa0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpsuVa0.png&h=6fc3b324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆你個街 第時就係咁"},{"pid":"43af4b964e1c7c710badc4c49cb5cc9afb57ab53","tid":1215301,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6e775ce6ce8346a3709c09a9363d47110c03bc","tid":1215301,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"*** 重要 ***<br />\n<br />\n一個鐘頭之前得到義務律師印證消息，公立醫院入面有人畀警察拉左。<br />\n<br />\n嗱，即係咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果你受傷入院求醫，我地醫護人員需要知道你嘅injury mechanism：例如，究竟你係畀子彈打中、定係畀支棍仆親等等。呢啲資訊對醫護人員嚟講，係有用嘅。<br />\n<br />\n但至於你本人係抗爭者、路人、暴徒、警察定黑社會，以及當時你點解會出現喺現場、點解會畀人打等等，其實呢啲資訊唔係必要，亦都medically irrelevant。<br />\n<br />\n記住，醫生護士唔係差人，我地冇權迫你講嘢，尤其一啲唔關事嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n記住，醫院唔單止得醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n醫院，就同呢個世界其他地方一樣，乜人都有。<br />\n<br />\n#我上面講左啲咩大家參詳吓<br />\n<br />\n#有乜野可以講<br />\n#有乜野唔應該講<br />\n<br />\n#保護自己<br />\n#免受傷害<br />\n#受傷一定要求醫<br />\n#但入左醫院都要繼續識保護自己㗎<br />\n<br />\nby 黃任匡"},{"pid":"29e801706036f0ea837c1148d03330835bbdba4d","tid":1215301,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"記得換埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鞋</span>"},{"pid":"96f647c39d16a85ba1149c3e9637bb744fe1e985","tid":1215301,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29e801706036f0ea837c1148d03330835bbdba4d","tid":1215301,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"記得換埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鞋</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"著耐咗咪買新鞋<br />\n唔想嘅咪借下波鞋比朋友著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}